USAGES:

    <screen mode="FADE_IN"
            (o) duration="$FADE_DURATION"
            (o) color="$FADE_COLOR" />

            $FADE_DURATION          - How long, in ms, the fade-in takes, default is 2500
            $FADE_COLOR             - Optional, what color to fade into, default is black


    <screen mode="FADE_OUT"
            (o) duration="$FADE_DURATION" />

            $FADE_DURATION          - Optional, How long, in ms, the fade-out takes, default is 2500